snippet.title: Cabin Escape: Alice's Story - Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Glitch Games is excited to announce Cabin Escape: Alice's Story. A short, free prologue to the Forever Lost series.

Don't worry though, you do not need to have played any of the Forever Lost games to enjoy this game. It will only enhance your experience of the Forever Lost world.
